  apply T.imp_closed (ѕЖ := ѕИ);
  . exact orIntroR;
  . assumption;
```

This is similar to `mem_orIntroL`, but if `ѕИ` is in the theory `T`, then `ѕЖ вИ® ѕИ` is also in `T`.

